Package: HerbLeafAnalyzer
Type: Package
Title: Plant Leaf Analysis Tools for Medicinal Herbs
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2024-04-15
Author: Sindayigaya Jean Marie Vianney
Description: Provides tools for analyzing medicinal herb leaves, including functions to load data, plot color distributions, calculate leaf areas, compare leaf shapes, and display herb characteristics in a tabular format.
